\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{ij}\lambda_{ij}X^{i}F^{j}=\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}\lambda_{i0}X^{i}+F(\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}\sum_{j=1}^{r-1}\lambda_{ij}X^{i}F^{j})$
\end_inset

, luego debe ser 
\begin_inset Formula $F\mid\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}\lambda_{i0}X^{i}$
\end_inset

