\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\overline{X^{n}F^{j}}=\overline{F^{j+1}}-\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}F_{i}\overline{X^{i}F^{j}}.
\]

\end_inset

Entonces, para 
\begin_inset Formula $j=r-1$
\end_inset

